This paper is about a machine learning algorithm, specifically Gradient Boosting Machine (GBM), which is commonly used in supervised learning tasks. Therefore, the most likely sub-category is cs.LG (Machine Learning), followed by cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence) and cs.DS (Data Structures and Algorithms) as they are also related to machine learning. The paper also mentions the use of GBM in computer vision (cs.CV) and neural networks (cs.NE), which are also possible sub-categories.
